from sympy.ntheory import digits
def F(n): return n if (b:=sum(d:=list(map(int, str(n)))))<2 else sum(di*10**i for i, di in enumerate(digits(n, b)[:0:-1]))
def a(n):
    c, seen = 0, set()
    while n not in seen: n, c, seen = F(n), c+1, seen | {n}
    return c
